Date: 1996-11-28

Title: A U(1) Gauge Theory for Antisymmetric Tensor Fields

Authors: Shinichi Deguchi, Tadahito Nakajima, and Hideomi Totsuka Atomic

(Energy Reserch Institute, Nihon University)Comments: 8 pages, TeX

Journal-ref: Prog.Theor.Phys. 97 (1997) 357-362

We show that a U(1) gauge theory defined in the configuration space forclosed p-branes yields the gauge theory of a massless rank-(p+1)antisymmetric tensor field and the Stueckelberg formalism for a massive vectorfield.